    <title>markdown初体验</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/posts/a675233b/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/posts/a675233b/</id>
    <published>2020-08-19T03:12:04.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-08-19T08:33:09.752Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="特点"><a href="#特点" class="headerlink" title="特点"></a>特点</h3><ul><li>兼容html、css语法</li><li>特殊字符自动转换<ul><li>如：<code>&amp;copy;</code>会变成&copy;</li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="语法"><a href="#语法" class="headerlink" title="语法"></a>语法</h3><blockquote><p><strong>在使用markdown语法时，需要在语法符号后面打个空格</strong></p></blockquote><h4 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h4><p><strong>越往后越小</strong></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line">.</span><br><span class="line">.</span><br><span class="line">.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">###### 六级标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="文本"><a href="#文本" class="headerlink" title="文本"></a>文本</h4><p><strong>使用两个相同符号将文本包裹即可</strong></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*斜体1*</span> <span class="emphasis">_斜体2_</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**粗体1**</span> <span class="strong">__粗体2__</span></span><br><span class="line">~~ 删除线 ~~</span><br><span class="line">==高亮==</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>斜体1</em> <em>斜体2</em><br><strong>粗体1</strong> <strong>粗体2</strong><br><del>删除线</del></p><h4 id="脚注"><a href="#脚注" class="headerlink" title="脚注"></a>脚注</h4><p><strong>脚注自动被搬运到最后面，请到文章末尾查看，并且脚注后方的链接可以直接跳转回到加注的地方</strong></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">^1</span>]:<span class="link">脚注1</span></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">^T</span>]:<span class="link">脚注T</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h4><p><strong>当混合使用时，中间会出现大量空白</strong></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">有序列表</span><br><span class="line">1.有序</span><br><span class="line">2.有序</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">无序列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 无序</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 无序</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 无序</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>有序列表</p><ol><li>有序</li><li>有序</li></ol><p>无序列表</p><ul><li>无序 *</li></ul><ul><li>无序 -</li></ul><ul><li>无序 +</li></ul><h4 id="区域块"><a href="#区域块" class="headerlink" title="区域块"></a>区域块</h4><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 引用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">`内嵌代码`</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​<span class="code">```多行代码```</span></span><br><span class="line">或者<span class="code">```加一个回车键</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">或者```&lt;代码类型&gt;加一个回车键</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>这是引用</p></blockquote><p><code>这是内嵌代码</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是多行代码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="分隔线"><a href="#分隔线" class="headerlink" title="分隔线"></a>分隔线</h4><p><strong>三个及以上相同符号（除了空格外行内不能有其它元素）</strong></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">****</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> <span class="emphasis">* *</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> - -</span><br><span class="line">----</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>这是分隔线</p><hr><h4 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h4><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">大致模板：</span><br><span class="line">鼠标提示可不使用，使用时前面记得留个空格</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">所展示的名字</span>](<span class="link">url &quot;鼠标悬停时的提示&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">bilibili</span>](<span class="link">https://www.bilibili.com/ &quot;这是B站的链接&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">进阶版：</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">id</span>]: <span class="link">url &quot;xxx&quot;  在任意位置定义（：后需要留空格）</span></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">bilibili2</span>][<span class="symbol">id</span>]  需要使用时拿来即用</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">自动链接:</span><br><span class="line">将文本视作url链接</span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">url</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/" title="这是B站的链接">bilibili</a></p><p><a href="http://www.bilibili.com/" title="这是B站链接">bilibili2</a></p><p><a href="http://bilibili.com/">http://bilibili.com</a></p><h4 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h4><ul><li><p><strong>直接拖进去自动生成</strong></p></li><li><p><strong><em>手动输入</em> 与链接用法几乎一致，只是前面多了”!”</strong></p></li></ul><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">图片替代文本</span>](<span class="link">url &quot;鼠标停留时的提示&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">id</span>]: <span class="link">url &quot;xxx&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">text</span>][<span class="symbol">id</span>]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">网络图片：</span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">img</span>](<span class="link">https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/article/956400925abfcde09279c249810321e9bdbb4d9a.jpg@1320w_826h.webp &#x27;阿库娅&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">本地图片：</span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">img</span>](<span class="link">E:/Desktop/akuya.jpg &#x27;阿库娅&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/article/956400925abfcde09279c249810321e9bdbb4d9a.jpg@1320w_826h.webp" alt="图片" title="阿库娅" style="zoom: 25%;" /><img src="E:/Desktop/akuya.jpg" alt="img" title="阿库娅" style="zoom:25%;" /><h4 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h4><p><strong>原生有点麻烦，不如直接右键插入表格</strong></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">第一行为各个列的表名称。第二行为下面内容的对齐方式，使用：进行标记。两个冒号加上减号 (-) 表示居中，减号后面是：表示居右，默认居左</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">| cloth         | price         |color  |</span><br><span class="line">| ------------- |:-------------:| -----:|</span><br><span class="line">| 衣服           | 16R     | 红 |</span><br><span class="line">| 裤子           | 6R      |   蓝 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th>cloth</th><th align="center">price</th><th align="right">color</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>衣服</td><td align="center">16R</td><td align="right">红</td></tr><tr><td>裤子</td><td align="center">6R</td><td align="right">蓝</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h3 id=&quot;特点&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#特点&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;特点&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;特点&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;兼容html、css语法&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;特殊字符自动转换&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;如：&lt;code&gt;&amp;amp;copy;&lt;/code&gt;</summary>
      
    
    
    
